title: Spectacular Corner Unit with Downtown Views, Balcony, Quiet Location!
posting_body: ['Borealis is a walkable, bikeable retreat in the vibrant North Loop neighborhood.', 'Featuring modern, upgraded interiors, beautiful (and functional!)', 'floor plans, and superior customer service, Borealis has received rave reviews from happy residents since opening its doors in March 2018.', 'Visit our Google page or read more about the building here: <URL>', '#607 -- Plan Q', 'Plan Q is a two bed, two bath layout available on the 6th floor with stunning Minneapolis skyline views.', ' This unit features two walls of floor-to-ceiling windows, a private balcony, an expansive kitchen island, and bedrooms on opposite ends.', ' Finishes include black granite countertops, white Shaker cabinetry, and warm maple vinyl plank flooring.', ' Natural light pours into this spacious corner home (Photos of comparable space.)', 'For info on amenities and to apply: <URL>', 'For your Instagram fix: @borealisnorthloop', 'Prices subject to change.', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- North Loop -- Warehouse District -- NE -- Northeast -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction']
